and acted as a Portfolio Manager for two investment funds. His extensive experience in the asset management industry includes receiving FMA licensing as Deputy Managing Director in 2014. Additionally, he was responsible for discretionary asset allocation and global fund selection. He also founded and led his own investment advisory and portfolio management company.</p></div><!--/$--></div><!--/$--></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mfejp2y9" role="" class="PiVxGu MDrwHQ comp-mfejp2y9 wixui-box" dir="ltr"><div aria-hidden="true" class="yPXgy9 YqUfCX inner-box wixui-box"></div><div data-testid="responsive-container-content" class="comp-mfejp2y9-container"><!--$--><div id="comp-mfejp2yf1" class="ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mfejp2yf1 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_2 wixui-rich-text__text">Stefan Wiederkehr</h2></div><!--/$--></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mfejelzg" role="" class="PiVxGu MDrwHQ comp-mfejelzg-container comp-mfejelzg wixui-box" dir="ltr"><div aria-hidden="true" class="yPXgy9 YqUfCX inner-box wixui-box"></div><!--$--><div id="comp-mfejg3r8" class="comp-mfejg3r8 wixui-vector-image"><a data-testid="linkElement" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/karin-wiederkehr-741b252b/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="aeyn4z"><div data-testid="svgRoot-comp-mfejg3r8" class="VDJedC l4CAhn"><?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
